snippet.title: Warface Raids - Pripyat
snippet.description:
The Warface squad is going into the most atmospheric abandoned city on the planet! The completely new enemies, unexpected dangers, and unpredictable twists and turns will leave you utterly speechless!

Subscribe to the channel: https://vk.cc/c0BDOQ
===========================================
Join the ranks of Warface, a free-to-play shooter for PC, PS4, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch!

Play now: https://warface.com​

Stay with us on other platforms: https://taplink.cc/warfacegameofficial

===========================================
Warface is a free online multiplayer shooter.

Subscribe to the channel to not miss news about the game, announcements of new game events, reviews of new weapons, maps, and content, streams with bloggers, developer diaries, as well as broadcasts of eSports tournaments. Likes and comments are welcome!
